arasu vidumurai , is an upcoming tamil romance film written and directed by c.balasubramaniyam.the film will star rajesh , elumalai , delhi ganesh , dr.vincent therraisnathan.the story of the film revolves around a small town . the film is produced by s.v.films & cbs cineinternational and features background score and soundtrack composed by thomas rathnam with cinematography handled by anbarasu .